properties.headline: Air Quality Alert issued January 22 at 9:11AM MST by NWS Pocatello ID
properties.description:
Air quality has improved significantly across the area. Therefore
the Idaho Department of Environmental Quality has cancelled the
air quality advisory.

For more information please access the departments
website at http://airquality.deq.idaho.gov

This statement is issued by the Idaho Department of Environmental
Quality, Air Quality Division, Pocatello Idaho Regional Office.
Contact at 208 236 6160.

NWSheadline: THE AIR QUALITY ADVISORY FOR FRANKLIN COUNTY HAS BEEN LIFTED BY THE IDAHO DEPARTMENT OF ENVIRONMENTAL QUALITY
